{"tid":597092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事有蹺蹺？有市民發現南生圍有一個疑似機油膠桶","createTime":"2018-03-18T09:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T12:28:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30206785e948c359a2832a433de14a6dbefa3266","tid":597092,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"有「香港人的後花園」及「雀鳥天堂」稱譽的元朗南生圍，上周接連遭遇火災，大片蘆葦及林木被毀。立法會議員鄺俊宇昨(17日)再收市民舉報，指發現南生圍有一個載著疑似機油的白色塑膠筒，認為事有蹺蹊，遂於昨日黃昏報警，據知警方已為該名市民錄取口供。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/photo/bkn-20180318110207644-0318_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180318154624\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180318%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180318110207644-0318_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180318154624&h=31b30b7d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇表示，繼日前有市民舉報案發時有可疑人物後，再有市民在南生圍發現可疑易燃物料，指如火災是人為而起，警方需盡快揪出縱火者以保護南生圍，而他亦正跟進事件。鄺續稱，計劃下周日(25日)聯同《萬人聯署，決不讓南生圍淪陷》行動組，在南生圍發動保衞行動，促社會關注保育南生圍，又指市民已無法容忍南生圍繼續被不斷破壞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/bkn-20180318110207644-0318_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180318%2Fbkn-20180318110207644-0318_00822_001.html&d=XdPyjybqQaprp66llt%2BsRdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fb6c2b77\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/bkn-20180318110207644-0318_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"118d7b6ded7bcc5ffab2299355f1d7fe6b945e11","tid":597092,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"南生圍首宗火警於上周一(12日)發生，焚燒17小時，至翌日(13日)早上被救熄，但至下午再起火，約3小時後救熄，廣闊的蘆葦床及草地被燒至焦黑，消防員事後調查發現火勢蔓延速度異常，且有多個火頭，相信起火原因有可疑，轉交警方跟進，警方經初步調查後把兩案合併，改列縱火案處理，由元朗警區重案組接手追查。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180318/photo/bkn-20180318110207644-0318_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180318154624\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180318%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180318110207644-0318_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180318154624&h=8549f7f0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n警方回覆東網查詢表示，昨日下午接獲市民報案，表示於南生圍發現一個載有液體的塑膠容器，警方派員到場，檢取相關證物作化驗。"},{"pid":"8ce08b7d038dc2f6311826bac3360266a92c0f51","tid":597092,"uid":22151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"地產佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbb1fe66d8f6383e70bad2d1084f91a5af95820","tid":597092,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"最後一定無事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85151dc759b463efc2b6b537ee90810d8aba9be","tid":597092,"uid":166434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"官商鄉黑<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"7b2270987b1bb651196aa5e87ba698f8cbf867a1","tid":597092,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}